  "title": "Financial Advisor – Fresh Graduates Welcome",
  "description": "<p>A leading financial advisory group is seeking energetic and ambitious individuals to join our team as Financial Advisors. If you are passionate about helping others achieve financial security and success, this is the opportunity for you.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum age 21</li>\n  <li>GCE A-Level (min. 2 H1 and 3 H2), Diploma, or Degree in any field</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Driven, disciplined, and self-motivated</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You Can Expect:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Structured training and mentoring program</li>\n  <li>Attractive allowance/commission and incentive schemes</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for rapid career progression</li>\n</ul>",
